   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify;"><span style="line-height:115%; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt;">Site : d&eacute;signe le site internet accessible &agrave; l&rsquo;adresse&nbsp;</span><a href="https://www.cazaexpert.fr" style="text-decoration:none;"><u><span style="line-height:115%; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; color:#1155cc;">https://www.citedex.fr</span></u></a><span style="line-height:115%; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height:115%; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt;">sur lequel est h&eacute;berg&eacute;e la Plateforme.</span></p>
