   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt;"><strong><span style="font-family:Arial;">ARTICLE 5 &ndash; MODALIT&Eacute; FINANCI&Egrave;RE DU SERVICE</span></strong></p>
   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:10pt;"><span style="font-family:Arial;">Le Particulier est inform&eacute; que l&rsquo;utilisation</span><span style="font-family:Arial;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:Arial;">du Site est gratuite.</span></p>
   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt;"><strong><span style="font-family:Arial;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>
   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt;"><strong><span style="font-family:Arial;">ARTICLE 6 &ndash; PROC&Eacute;DURE D&rsquo;ACC&Egrave;S &Agrave; L&apos;ABONNEMENT</span></strong></p>
   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:normal; font-size:10pt;"><span style="font-family:Arial;">La cr&eacute;ation d&rsquo;un Compte Abonn&eacute; est permise &agrave; toute personne physique, majeure et capable.</span></p>
   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:10pt;"><span style="font-family:Arial;">A ce titre, l&apos;utilisateur Particulier doit remplir un formulaire d&rsquo;inscription et fournir certaines donn&eacute;es. A ce titre, l&apos;utilisateur Particulier s&rsquo;engage &agrave; fournir des informations exactes, compl&egrave;tes, sinc&egrave;res et pr&eacute;cises.</span></p>
   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:10pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:10pt;"><span style="font-family:Arial;">L&rsquo;Utilisateur Particulier devra renseigner notamment les informations suivantes :</span></p>
   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:-18pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:10pt;"><span style="font-family:Arial;">❖</span><span style="width:10.5pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:Arial;">Nom et pr&eacute;nom ;</span></p>
   <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-left:36pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-indent:-18pt; text-align:justify; line-height:115%; font-size:10pt;"><span style="font-family:Arial;">❖</span><span style="width:10.5pt; font:7pt 'Times New Roman'; display:inline-block;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family:Arial;">Num&eacute;ro de t&eacute;l&eacute;phone ;</span></p>
